# Experimental!
F    ← ˜∘
C    ← "23456789TJQKA"
S    ← "CDHS"
I    ← ⊂@_ C
Deck ← °⍆♭₂⊞⊂C S # Shuffled
⊃↙↘26Deck

Round ← (
  ⊙F∩(⊃↙↘1)                            # First pair
  ⍢(∩˜⊂⊙F⊙⊙⊙F ⊙⊙∩(⍣(⊃↙↘2|["__" "__"])) # Keep drawing...
  | =∩(⊢⊢)                             # ...until winner.
  )
  ⨬˜⊂⍜⊙F˜⊂⊃(>∩(⨂I⊢⊢)|°⍆⊂) # Give cards to winner.
)
⍢(Round⟜₂(⊂∩⧻)|>0×∩⧻) # Play rounds until exhausted.
⊃(⧻|+1\+˙⊜⧻+2▽⊸≠0±/-⍉)
&p$"_ rounds played.\nLead changed hands at rounds: _"
